<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-the-contrary">on the contrary</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>正相反；恰恰相反：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He thought his marketing plan was perfect, but on the contrary, it was not and it failed.
他以为自己的营销计划完美无缺，而事实恰恰相反，这个计划不仅不完美，还徒劳无功。</p><footer>人教③ – 3</footer></div></div>